metadata.name: Sky Club Passport
metadata.description: The Level 3 Sky Club Passport NFT is the ultimate status symbol, reserved for the most elite and discerning individuals. As a Level 3 holder, you will have access to the most exclusive events and experiences, as well as unparalleled networking opportunities with other high-profile individuals. This NFT represents the pinnacle of luxury, prestige, and exclusivity, and is a testament to your status as one of the most successful and influential individuals in the world.
